text: Tooth Fairy is a 2010 American Canadian fantasy-comedy movie directed by Michael Lembeck and starring Dwayne Johnson, Ashley Judd, Julie Andrews, Stephen Merchant, Ryan Sheckler, Billy Crystal. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. == Release date == *USA - January 22, 2010 *UK - May 28, 2010 & February 8, 2013 (re-release) *Egypt - November 21, 2012 == Other websites == * * Category:2010 comedy movies Category:2010 fantasy movies Category:American fantasy-comedy movies Category:Canadian fantasy movies Category:Canadian comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Michael Lembeck Category:20th Century Fox movies
